reviewText: I am a HUGE fan of Beavis and Butt-Head. And I simply couldn't be happier! This box set comes with 122 episodes, the movie, tons of extras that I still havn't gotten through, and not to mention a bobblehead of both beavis and butt-head. If you're a true fan of Beavis and Butt-Head then Mike Judge's genius box set will satisfy you.

My husband and I love the box set so much, we bought one for my brother.  The episodes are hilarious and socially relevant.  The extras are amazing and offer great behind-the-scenes info.  Not to mention the bobble-heads are not to be missed.  A must-have, one-stop collection.

this i an awesome beavis and butthead collection, plus it comes with the movie and  2 bobbleheads.the only downside on the episodes is the music videos aren't on the cartoons like back when it was on MTV, but there is a seperate disc with music videos and B&B's commentary of them..
